---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { u } from '../../lib/url';
import SectionBreath from '../../components/SectionBreath.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="For public administration · Thorn"
  description="Digitalisation work for Romanian city halls, county councils and deconcentrated services. Funding-aligned, procurement-compliant, named accountability."
  lang="en"
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="surface-light pt-12 md:pt-20 pb-16 md:pb-24">
    <div class="container-page">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-y-8 md:gap-x-10">
        <div class="md:col-span-9">
          <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700 mb-8 md:mb-10">
            <span class="font-mono">001</span>
            <span class="mx-3 text-ink-300">·</span>
            For public administration
          </div>
          <h1 class="font-sans font-medium text-display-1 text-ink-900 hang tracking-tight">
            The money is there.<br/>
            <span class="text-ink-400">The strategy usually isn't.</span>
          </h1>
        </div>

        <aside class="md:col-span-3 md:pt-32 md:border-l md:border-forest-100 md:pl-6">
          <div class="eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-3">Audience</div>
          <div class="text-ink-900 text-body-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            City halls<br/>
            County councils<br/>
            Deconcentrated services
          </div>

          <div class="eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-3">Coverage</div>
          <div class="text-ink-900 text-body-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Romania-wide
          </div>

          <div class="eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-3">Primary contact</div>
          <div class="text-ink-900 text-body-sm leading-relaxed">
            Ioana Drăghici
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 md:mt-16 max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-body-lg text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
          PNRR Component 7. Regional Programme Nord-Vest. DigiLocal. NIS2 compliance funding. Hundreds of millions of euros flowing into municipal digitalisation, often unspent or spent on the wrong thing because the gap between "we need to digitalise" and "here is the project that earns the grant" is wider than it looks.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The 3-step path -->
  <section class="surface-medium section">
    <div class="container-page">

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <div class="md:col-span-4">
          <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700 mb-3">002 · Engagement</div>
          <h2 class="font-sans font-medium text-display-2 text-ink-900 leading-tight tracking-tight hang">
            Three steps.<br/>
            <span class="text-ink-400">Three contracts.</span>
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-8 md:pt-4">
          <p class="text-body-lg text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
            Each step is a separate, properly procured contract. No fragmentation, no surprises, no commitment to step two until step one delivers something useful.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">

        <article class="card-secondary">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:gap-10">
            <div class="md:col-span-3 flex flex-col">
              <div class="step-numeral-lg mb-4">01</div>
              <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700">Assessment</div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-6">
              <p class="text-ink-800 text-body leading-relaxed mb-5">
                One to three days on site. A written 15 to 25 page report your Local Council can review. Identifies the funding lines you currently qualify for and what the realistic next interventions are.
              </p>
              <dl class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-body-sm">
                <div>
                  <dt class="font-mono text-eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-1">Duration</dt>
                  <dd class="text-ink-900">1-2 weeks</dd>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <dt class="font-mono text-eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-1">Fee</dt>
                  <dd class="text-ink-900">Fixed</dd>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <dt class="font-mono text-eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-1">Procurement</dt>
                  <dd class="text-ink-900">Single</dd>
                </div>
              </dl>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-3 md:pl-6 md:border-l md:border-forest-100">
              <div class="eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-2">Output</div>
              <p class="text-ink-700 text-body-sm leading-relaxed">
                Written report. Roadmap. Prioritised list of interventions costed to thresholds.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card-secondary">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:gap-10">
            <div class="md:col-span-3 flex flex-col">
              <div class="step-numeral-lg mb-4">02</div>
              <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700">Funding application</div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-6">
              <p class="text-ink-800 text-body leading-relaxed mb-5">
                If the assessment surfaces a clear funding fit, we draft the technical sections of the grant application. Submitted by your team or with our support, depending on what's allowed by the procedure.
              </p>
              <dl class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-body-sm">
                <div>
                  <dt class="font-mono text-eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-1">Duration</dt>
                  <dd class="text-ink-900">2-4 weeks</dd>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <dt class="font-mono text-eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-1">Fee</dt>
                  <dd class="text-ink-900">Fixed</dd>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <dt class="font-mono text-eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-1">Stage</dt>
                  <dd class="text-ink-900">Optional</dd>
                </div>
              </dl>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-3 md:pl-6 md:border-l md:border-forest-100">
              <div class="eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-2">Output</div>
              <p class="text-ink-700 text-body-sm leading-relaxed">
                Technical sections of the grant submission. Project plan. Compliance documentation.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card-secondary">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:gap-10">
            <div class="md:col-span-3 flex flex-col">
              <div class="step-numeral-lg mb-4">03</div>
              <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700">Implementation</div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-6">
              <p class="text-ink-800 text-body leading-relaxed mb-5">
                When funding lands, we deliver. Single team, named technical lead, end-to-end accountability. Recurring maintenance included for the first year.
              </p>
              <dl class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-body-sm">
                <div>
                  <dt class="font-mono text-eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-1">Duration</dt>
                  <dd class="text-ink-900">3-9 mo</dd>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <dt class="font-mono text-eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-1">Contract</dt>
                  <dd class="text-ink-900">Single</dd>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <dt class="font-mono text-eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-1">SEAP</dt>
                  <dd class="text-ink-900">Scoped right</dd>
                </div>
              </dl>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-3 md:pl-6 md:border-l md:border-forest-100">
              <div class="eyebrow text-ink-500 mb-2">Output</div>
              <p class="text-ink-700 text-body-sm leading-relaxed">
                Working system, documentation, runbooks, year-one maintenance.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Funding lines - dark inversion -->
  <section class="surface-dark section">
    <div class="container-page">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <div class="md:col-span-4">
          <div class="eyebrow text-forest-300 mb-3">003 · Funding context</div>
          <h2 class="font-sans font-medium text-display-2 text-cream-50 leading-tight tracking-tight hang">
            What's actually<br/>fundable.
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-8 md:pt-4">
          <p class="text-body-lg text-cream-100/80 leading-relaxed">
            The landscape changes every few months. This is the current map. We update it as windows open and close.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="card-secondary">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4 pb-4 border-b border-forest-700">
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-lg text-cream-50 tracking-tight">DigiLocal (OUG 56/2024)</h3>
            <div class="font-mono tabular text-eyebrow text-forest-300">75K-175K RON</div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-cream-100/80 text-body-sm leading-relaxed">
            Direct grants for digitalisation in communes. Open windows tied to the OUG calendar. Most accessible funding line right now for smaller administrations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-secondary">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4 pb-4 border-b border-forest-700">
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-lg text-cream-50 tracking-tight">PNRR Component 7</h3>
            <div class="font-mono tabular text-eyebrow text-forest-300">Up to M RON</div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-cream-100/80 text-body-sm leading-relaxed">
            "Digital transformation" envelope. Tighter eligibility, longer application, larger scope. Best for cities and counties with a digitalisation strategy already in place or under development.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-secondary">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4 pb-4 border-b border-forest-700">
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-lg text-cream-50 tracking-tight">PR Nord-Vest 2021-2027</h3>
            <div class="font-mono tabular text-eyebrow text-forest-300">Project-based</div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-cream-100/80 text-body-sm leading-relaxed">
            Region-specific operational programme covering Cluj, Bistrița-Năsăud, Maramureș, Sălaj, Satu Mare and Bihor counties. Smart-specialisation, public administration modernisation, citizen services.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-secondary">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4 pb-4 border-b border-forest-700">
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-lg text-cream-50 tracking-tight">NIS2 (Law 124/2025)</h3>
            <div class="font-mono tabular text-eyebrow text-forest-300">Tier-dependent</div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-cream-100/80 text-body-sm leading-relaxed">
            Administrations classified as "essential entities" under NIS2 face hard compliance deadlines. Dedicated funding lines are being announced through DNSC. Worth assessing your classification before the deadline becomes the strategy.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionBreath label="Common questions" tone="light" />

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="surface-light section">
    <div class="container-page">

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10 mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <div class="md:col-span-4">
          <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700 mb-3">004 · FAQ</div>
          <h2 class="font-sans font-medium text-display-2 text-ink-900 leading-tight tracking-tight hang">
            What we get<br/>asked first.
          </h2>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="border-t border-forest-100 pt-8">
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-xl text-ink-900 mb-3 tracking-tight">
              "We already have Regista / Avansis / CityManager. Why do we need anything else?"
            </h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 text-body leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
              You probably don't need a replacement. You need the system you have to talk to ANAF, to the cadastre, to your accounting layer, to the dashboards a Mayor actually reads. Most of our work for primării is integration and data layer, not rip-and-replace.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-t border-forest-100 pt-8">
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-xl text-ink-900 mb-3 tracking-tight">
              "We don't have a budget."
            </h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 text-body leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
              Worth checking that. DigiLocal grants, PNRR Component 7, Regional Programme Nord-Vest and NIS2 compliance lines all have active or imminent windows. Our assessment identifies the lines you currently qualify for. If the answer is none, we say so on the first day.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-t border-forest-100 pt-8">
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-xl text-ink-900 mb-3 tracking-tight">
              "Our systems aren't online. Our staff aren't ready."
            </h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 text-body leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
              That's exactly the starting position the assessment is built for. Staff training is included in any implementation scope, and we sequence the technical work so the operational change is gradual rather than abrupt.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-t border-forest-100 pt-8">
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-xl text-ink-900 mb-3 tracking-tight">
              "How long does this actually take?"
            </h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 text-body leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
              Assessment: one to two weeks. Funding application: two to four weeks. Implementation: three to nine months depending on scope. Recurring maintenance: ongoing once the system is live.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-t border-forest-100 pt-8">
            <h3 class="font-sans font-semibold text-xl text-ink-900 mb-3 tracking-tight">
              "Will you fragment the contract to fit it under a threshold?"
            </h3>
            <p class="text-ink-700 text-body leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
              No. Article 11 of Law 98/2016 prohibits splitting contracts to dodge procurement thresholds and we won't propose it. If your scope is bigger than one threshold, we run the right SEAP procedure for the right size. It takes a few weeks longer and it stays clean.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Compliance ribbon -->
  <section class="surface-dark py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="container-page">
      <dl class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 md:gap-6">
        <div>
          <dt class="eyebrow text-forest-300 mb-2">Procurement</dt>
          <dd class="text-cream-50 text-body font-medium">SEAP registered, DUAE-ready</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt class="eyebrow text-forest-300 mb-2">Legal compliance</dt>
          <dd class="text-cream-50 text-body font-medium">Law 242/2022 specialised</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt class="eyebrow text-forest-300 mb-2">Contract integrity</dt>
          <dd class="text-cream-50 text-body font-medium">Article 11, Law 98/2016</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
          <dt class="eyebrow text-forest-300 mb-2">Data protection</dt>
          <dd class="text-cream-50 text-body font-medium">GDPR, Romanian residency</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="surface-light section">
    <div class="container-page text-center">
      <div class="eyebrow text-forest-700 mb-6">005</div>
      <h2 class="font-sans font-medium text-display-2 text-ink-900 leading-tight mb-10 hang max-w-2xl mx-auto tracking-tight">
        Worth a half-hour<br/>conversation?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-body-lg text-ink-700 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-12">
        Tell us your primărie, the rough scope of what you're thinking about, and what (if anything) has been tried before. We'll come back with the funding lines that look like a fit and what an assessment would cover.
      </p>
      <a href={u('/en/contact')} class="btn-primary">
        Start a conversation
        <svg class="btn-arrow" width="14" height="10" viewBox="0 0 14 10" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M0 5h12M8 1l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
